name: Macabre Love Card Duo
description:
For the couple who's love is romantic but with that appreciation for dark humor. These definitely will make a memorable markâ€¦ certainly not for every couple- which is precisely why they are two of our favorites! Perfect for an anniversary, birthday, Halloween, Valentines or just because.


1- Darkly Beloved Vulture Corpse card, reads:
"If you were a corpse and I was a vulture I would pick your bones clean"

1-  Mosquito Love Bitten Card, reads:
"If I was a mosquito I'd only have bites for you!"

A2 cards (4.25" x 5.5" when closed.) Flat printed (not letterpress) on high quality correspondence stock. Blank inside. Paired with an envelope.

name: Emerald Cat Letterpress Tags
description:
Meow! We are cat-nip crazy about these hot off the press fancy feline tags in beautiful emerald & gorgeous mint. Kitty is prancing in a sea of deco bloom-wheels and is gussied up by a calligraphy flourish. We left these sentiment free so they can be used for birthdays, favor or gift tags, mini-notes, place cards, craft or toy bin labels--- anything you can think of really.

Tags measure 2" x 3.25" and are letterpress printed on high quality correspondence stock. For larger quantities (for events or favor tags, etc.) please contact us.

name: Jane Austen's Mr.Darcy
description:
Jane Austen's Pride & Prejudice is about as crucial as food & water around Pearl & Marmalade land. Give this card to your fellow friends who have met their Mr.Darcy (perhaps after a string of Wickhams!).

This card is letterpressed with our original sentiment "Congratulations on finding your Mr.Darcy". A dashing Darcy on horseback rides in from Pemberley amidst swags of cut-flowers & scallop rosettes. Printed in radish and pale grey. Just right for an engagement, bridal shower, anniversary or newly formed couple card.

How do you take your Fitzwilliam Darcy? We like ours with a touch of Firth. Colin Firth that is.

1- A1 sized card (3.5" " x 4.875" when closed), blank inside, letterpress printed on highest quality correspondence coverstock, paired with envelope

Print, photos, & patterns etc. represented here and elsewhere are protected by copyright(2011)

name: Grasshopper Toile Noteset
description:
Hello Hoppers! Design features a toile of sorts made of echo grey vines, sunny yellow leaves and dashing minty green grasshoppers.
Just right for everyday letters or use them for baby or bridal shower thank you notes or prizes!

Set of 6 notecards & envelopes, A1 sized (3 1/2" x 5" when closed), Please note, these are not letterpressed: flat printing on highest quality correspondence card-stock.

name: Pod Blooms Letterpress Note Set
description:
Bright clementine orange pod blooms and linen colored sprigs & stems adorn these letterpress note cards.

Perfect for everyday stationery, these would also make lovely recipe cards, thank you cards or hostess gifts.

Note set includes 6 flat cards, A2 size (4.25" x 5.5"). Letterpress printed on highest quality correspondence stock. Paired with envelopes.

name: Feather & Fern Folded Notes
description:
A striking ethereal take on our classic Amidst Routes print, this time as folded blank cards. Imagery of lace & floral snippets with geometric diamond forms surround a balancing act of a delicate feather and lush fern. These letterpress keepsakes are blank inside making them suitable for all occasions.

Set of 6 cards- A2 size (4.25" x 5.5" when closed). Letterpress printed with mossy spring green & soft echo grey inks on high quality correspondence stock & paired with envelopes.

name: Earnestly Abe Print
description:
Oh wise Mr.Lincoln and your honest advice.
When we have those weary moments of sullen doubt these words of Abe's remind us of all the delightful heights to come. And when that song and dance is here we want to be standing tall and at the ready!

This art print has the encouraging quote "I will prepare and some day my chance will come". It is adorned with imagery of a relic pocket-watch flanked by scarlet damask cabin blooms, cocoa hued watchful winged critters and skeleton keys.

Perfectly sized to fit a standard 8"x10" frame (not included), printed with flat archival ink on high quality coverstock. Comes packaged sleeved & with a backing making it perfect for gifting.

name: Amidst Routes Print
description:
Here's our much blogged about Amidst Routes print that was also featured in Readymade Magazine. This limited edition print features dear botanical imagery surrounded by geometric diamonds and antique lace bit-lettes. A stem of allium has grown a sprig of rosemary for roots while a tick-tocked flip-flopped bloom (a ranunculus or peony) sprouted a stem of mint for routes.

Hand numbered and uniquely packaged in cellophane with a grey giant tag backing to make this perfectly packaged for gift giving. Looks lovely framed- just right for a kitchen, a vignette of other artwork or on a wall needing some love!

Nab one while you can we only printed 266.
Print measures 5" x 7", Letterpress printed in echo grey and mustard ink

Print, photos, & patterns etc. represented here and elsewhere are protected by copyright(2011)

name: Letterpress Critters Card Set
description:
Keep a little stash of greeting cards on hand to help in a pinch! Save by buying a set of 3 of our best loved letterpress cards. Foldover A1 size (3 1/2" x 5" when closed) you'll receive 1 of each:

Regal Birthday Cat: A positively royal crowned feline- caption reads  "Happy Birthday! Lounge around and be regal all day."  Coral and grey inks on high quality correspondence stock. Blank inside.

Seed Pod Pigeon: Features a dashing pigeon in a shower of maple seed helicopter pods. Fun typesetting lends the message "Happy Birthday to you". Great for lads or ladies! Spring green & echo grey inks on high quality correspondence stock. Blank inside.

Llama Spit: An expressive llama proclaims "I miss you so much I could spit" in a boxy font with deco geometric shapes. Nothing like a chuckle sent from afar to brighten your recipient's day! Cherry & linen inks on high quality correspondence stock. Blank inside.

name: Numbers! Numbers! Print
description:
This playful print is features numbers and charming graphics.
Letterpress printed on white correspondence stock in deco blue and pebble grey ink. Numbered 0-9 with different icons for each number including a dog (retriever), bunny rabbit, butterfly trio, snail, seahorse, sailboat, elephant and fox.

Print measures 5" x 7". Each print is hand numbered. Better nab one soon. This is a limited edition print and we only have 247. Packaged with a mock giant-tag backing, it's ready for giving to a special little one or any kid at heart.

Would look great in a nursery, child's room, classroom, or a perfect gift for new Moms.

name: Someone Quite Dear Print
description:
When those dreary days hit, whose love saves your day from gloomy frowns? For moms and dads, new nieces, best friends, sweet ladies or your favorite lads, give one of these to the Dearest Someones in your life!

A charming bear with a polka dot parasol is caught in a downpour of raindrops and hearts...Accented with a sketchy edge of blooming lace and flower bits along the bottom. The sentiment "your love saves my day" in handwriting font

Letterpressed in a striking combination of Cocoa Brown and Radish inks. Each print is hand numbered and packaged in a protective sleeve w/backing, an edition of 302.

Measures 5" x 7" and fits a standard frame perfectly.

name: Scriptly Thanks Noteset
description:
Our well mannered Scriptly Thanks note set features delicate lace imagery and an utterly sophisticated calligraphy font with the sentiment "Thank You". Letterpressed in swell clementine orange and echo-linen inks.

Set includes:
6 flat cards, A2 size (4.25" x 5.5") printed on highest quality correspondence stock, paired with envelopes.
Use these as everyday notes, wedding or baby shower thank you's, or noteworthy gifts the etiquette savvy!

name: Queen Anne's Lace Noteset
description:
This design is inspired by fond memories of picking handfuls of whispery Queen Anne's lace for mason jars in the barefoot summers of our youth. We can still smell that fresh green celery-like wildflower scent. Before our love of dahlias and peonies, this was our first favorite flower!

Stems of grey Queen Anne's lace intermingles with intricate coral star bursts that echo antique furniture brads.

Note set includes 6 flat cards, A1 size (3.5" x 4.875"). Letterpress printed on highest quality correspondence stock in grey and coral inks. Paired with envelopes.
